shops.name: Victory Tattoo
shops.desc: Victory Tattoo is West Nashville's premier tattoo shop. Victory Tattoo is a clean, sterile, comfortable environment boasting an impressive line up of some of Nashville's best tattooers.

shops.name: Gold Club Electric Tattoo
shops.desc: We specialize In all forms of tattooing.  Bright and bold traditional tattoos, vibrant new school, smooth and defined black and grey, precision script work, life like color realism, and the art of the cover up.

shops.name: Black 13 Tattoo Parlor
shops.desc: Black 13 Tattoo Parlor is located in Nashville Tennessee’s historic Cummins Station and offers a clean, comfortable, upscale environment with the finest artistry and customer experience.

shops.name: Grimm City Tattoo
shops.desc: All 5 of GrimmCity Tattoo artists are are very well rounded, versatile artist who can do a wide range of styles from realistic, new school/neo-traditional, classic tattoo style.

shops.name: Battleground Tattoo Parlour
shops.desc: Battleground Tattoo Parlour was created to serve historic Franklin Tennessee and the surrounding area with the best in custom, progressive tattooing.

shops.name: Nashville Ink Tattoo
shops.desc: The safety of our clients is of utmost importance at Nashville Ink Tattoo. We ensure that all tattoo and piercing instruments and materials are either thrown away or sterilized in a high-pressure, high-temperature autoclave after each use.

shops.name: Rebel Yell Tattoo & Social Club
shops.desc: Rebel Yell Tattoo is conveniently located about a half-mile south of downtown Nashville, on Fourth Avenue South. Owned and Operated by J. Evans, we are Nashville’s premiere Traditional based tattoo shop.

shops.name: Icon Body Piercing
shops.desc: We've been supplying Nashville and Murfreesboro with high quality tattooing, body piercing, and body jewelry since 1997. Our top priority is our customers. We give 110% to make sure that everyone feels comfortable and gets good work.

shops.name: Safe House Tattoo Studio
shops.desc: Our mission is to provide a safe place for both artist, and client to enjoy the world of tattoo art.

shops.name: Flash City Tattoo
shops.desc: Flash City Tattoo has been supplying Nashville with high quality tattoos of every style since September 2012.
